---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import ServiceCard from "../../components/ui/ServiceCard.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import c1 from "../../assets/pics/card-pic1.png";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Market Positioning for LearnTech Companies | TheLearnBetter.co"
  description="Position your education technology solution effectively in the market. We help learntech companies define their unique value proposition and stand out to schools, universities, and educational organizations."
>
  <div class="py-16 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl lg:py-24 lg:px-6">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <ServiceCard
        index={1}
        titleTop="Market"
        titleBottom="Positioning"
        img={c1}
        alt="Market Positioning for LearnTech"
        link="/services/market-positioning"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 mb-16">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium mb-6">Strategic Positioning for Education Technology</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          In the crowded education technology landscape, clear positioning is essential. We help learntech companies articulate their unique value proposition and differentiate themselves in the market.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          Our market positioning services focus on understanding your target audience—whether that's K-12 schools, higher education institutions, corporate learning departments, or educational organizations—and crafting messaging that resonates with their specific needs and challenges.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          We analyze competitive landscapes, identify market opportunities, and develop positioning strategies that make your learntech solution stand out to decision-makers in educational institutions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray rounded-2xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-6">What We Deliver</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="mr-3 w-6 h-6 mt-1 text-green flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Competitive analysis and market landscape mapping</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="mr-3 w-6 h-6 mt-1 text-green flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Unique value proposition development</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="mr-3 w-6 h-6 mt-1 text-green flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Target audience segmentation and persona development</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="mr-3 w-6 h-6 mt-1 text-green flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Messaging framework and positioning statement</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="mr-3 w-6 h-6 mt-1 text-green flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Go-to-market strategy aligned with your positioning</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-dark text-white rounded-2xl p-10 md:p-16 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium mb-6">Our Approach</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div>
          <div class="text-green text-5xl font-medium mb-3">01</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3">Research & Analysis</h3>
          <p class="text-gray">Deep dive into your market, competitors, and target audience to identify positioning opportunities.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-green text-5xl font-medium mb-3">02</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3">Strategy Development</h3>
          <p class="text-gray">Craft a differentiated positioning strategy that resonates with educational decision-makers.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-green text-5xl font-medium mb-3">03</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3">Implementation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray">Develop messaging frameworks and positioning assets for consistent market communication.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center bg-gray rounded-2xl p-10 md:p-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium mb-6">Ready to Position Your LearnTech Solution?</h2>
      <p class="mb-10 text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Let's discuss how strategic positioning can help your education technology company stand out and reach the right educational institutions.
      </p>
      <a href="/#contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-10 py-5 bg-dark text-white rounded-2xl hover:bg-green hover:text-dark transition-all font-medium text-xl">
        Start a Conversation
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
